sentences: Dave Klein (born May 31, 1979) is an American musician and punk rock bass player from Edmond, Oklahoma, United States.

Former bands include Black Flag, Good For You, The Proctologists, Bi-Products, P.D.B, From Parts Unknown, Jettison, Wretch Like Me (Owned & Operated Recordings 1997-2002), Euclid Crash, Bristol Park, On Again, and American Ruse.
